## Root Cause
The original analyze-drift.ts had hardcoded snapshots:
- `contractSnapshot.tables.profiles` included non-existent `is_test` column
- `txTypesInContract` included UI-only `FIRST_INVESTMENT`

These hardcoded values became stale and didn't reflect the actual contracts.

